node.text:
Listen to me very closely: if you want to be a boss, you’re going to have to learn to be independent & self-reliant. That’s right - I don’t care how old you are, if you want to be a boss, you have to be independent!

I’ve been telling you that knowledge is the new money, and this is your chance to get some FREE knowledge! Be sure to check out this episode of free summer school, and we’ll see you there!

📺 The full video is now on my YouTube Channel 👈🏾

node.text:
Look, y’all - the moment that we take responsibility for our lives is the moment that we gain control of our lives. You have to catch this one! When we stop blaming others, when we stop being a victim - that’s when we go to the next level!

We’ll talk all about how to overcome that victim mentality in today’s episode of free summer school: Knowledge Is The New Money! Get ready to take notes on this one, and I’ll see you there! Now you know, let’s GO!

📺 The full video is now on my YouTube Channel 👈🏾

node.text:
Listen, accidents happen… or do they? To be honest with you, there are no accidents in life. We have to start taking total ownership over our lives - and that’s what this episode of free summer school is all about!

Join us as we break down this super important topic and get you some of this knowledge! Remember, small steps, great distances. Now you know, let’s go!

📺 The full video is now on my YouTube Channel 👈🏾

node.title: No Accidents In Life | Summer School Series

node.text:
Listen to me very closely, y’all… the only person who needs to affirm you is YOU! Yup, you heard me! When I stopped living my life trying to impress other people, I went to another level. I had to learn to feel good about myself regardless of what other people thought - and that’s what I want to teach you to do, too!

Make sure you lock in on this episode of free summer school: Knowledge Is The New Money, and I’ll see you there. Together, we can make the rest of your life the best of your life.

📺 The full video is now on my YouTube Channel 👈🏾

node.title: Not Needing Affirmation | Summer School Series

node.text:
Can I be honest with you? As a grown man, I do everything I can to give back to my parents! I’m not saying you have to agree with everything your parents say, but I am saying that they do the best they can for you - and we have to respect that!

On this episode of free summer school, the squad and I chop it up about the relationship you have with your parents. This is an important topic, so don’t miss it! Remember, small steps, great distances. Now you know… Let’s go!

📺 The full video is now on my YouTube Channel 👈🏾

node.title: Relationship With Parents | Summer School Series

node.text:
Look, y’all - I know from experience that fear can be a strong emotion… but it ain’t stronger than you! In this episode of free summer school: Knowledge Is The New Money, my friends and I will be walking you through how to overcome your fears.

I’m not saying it will be easy, but I am saying you can, you will, and you must overcome! So - tune in to this episode of summer school, and remember: small steps, great distances… now you know, let’s go!

📺 The full video is now on my YouTube Channel 👈🏾

node.title: Dealing with Fear | Summer School Series

node.text: What a blessing to be able to speak to @libertyfootball . Not only was it great to pour into the young men but I also got a chance to hang out with staff member and @9to5millionaire son @legend9497. Also linked with @jacksonshirer. Ended up getting outta there a little late and just when It seemed as all hope was lost, they gassed up the private ✈️ for ya boy! S/o to @Coachfreeze for the love!

node.text:
Did you grab your tickets 🎟 yet? Swipe ⬅️ 

You SHOULD have the power and freedom to create the life that you want to live, and the life that you truly deserve.

Honestly, it’s easily achievable for anyone.

You SHOULD be able to keep an ever-growing action-taking momentum going so that you can effortlessly finish every task, project or goal you set your mind to.

That’s what I call “living life at 120%”.

🔺 One Conference
🔺 One City : Atlanta
🔺 September 25 - 26

Hurry - get you tickets now!! 120Series.com
Or
Click the link in my bio @etthehiphoppreacher

Tag 🏷 your friends and let me know when you have your ticket!

I have some questions for you:
🔸 Do you feel like you're all alone?
🔸 Do you feel like you need a team?
🔸 Do you feel like you need hope?
🔸 Do you feel like you need inspiration?
If you said yes to any of these questions then I will see you September 25-26 in Atlanta for the LIVE 120 Conference.

Tag a friend and go to 120series.com to grab your tickets or the link in my bio @etthehiphoppreacher 

Let me know who will be in the room if you have your tickets already!
